g.title: compound_stmt
g.text: compound_stmt: if_stmt | while_stmt | for_stmt | try_stmt | with_stmt | funcdef | classdef | decorated

g.title: small_stmt
g.text: small_stmt: (expr_stmt | print_stmt | del_stmt | pass_stmt | flow_stmt |import_stmt | global_stmt | exec_stmt | assert_stmt)

g.title: try_stmt
g.text: try_stmt: ('try' ':' suite ((except_clause ':' suite)+['else' ':' suite]['finally' ':' suite] |'finally' ':' suite))

g.title: if_stmt
g.text: if_stmt: 'if' test ':' suite ('elif' test ':' suite)* ['else' ':' suite]

g.title: suite
g.text: suite: simple_stmt | NEWLINE INDENT stmt+ DEDENT

g.title: varargslist
g.text: varargslist: ((fpdef ['=' test] ',')* ('*' NAME [',' '**' NAME] | '**' NAME) | fpdef ['=' test] (',' fpdef ['=' test])* [','])

g.title: flow_stmt
g.text: flow_stmt: break_stmt | continue_stmt | return_stmt | raise_stmt | yield_stmt
